<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About QuickChat</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .navbar {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .content-wrapper {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 5rem;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
      }

      .header {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #343a40;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        animation: fadeInDown 2s ease-in-out;
      }

      .sub-header {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #6c757d;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        animation: fadeInDown 2s ease-in-out 0.5s;
      }

      .content {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #343a40;
        line-height: 1.6;
        animation: fadeInUp 2s ease-in-out 1s;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background-color: #25d366;
        border-color: #25d366;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        animation: fadeInUp 2s ease-in-out 1.5s;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: #1ebc59;
        border-color: #1ebc59;
      }

      .animated-graphic {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -100px;
        width: 100%;
        height: 200px;
        background: url("path/to/your/graphic.svg") no-repeat center bottom;
        background-size: cover;
        animation: slideUp 3s ease-in-out 2s forwards;
      }

      @keyframes fadeInDown {
        0% {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(-20px);
        }
        100% {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      @keyframes fadeInUp {
        0% {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        100% {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      @keyframes slideUp {
        0% {
          transform: translateY(100%);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light fixed-top">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">QuickChat</a>
        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-bs-toggle="collapse"
          data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
          aria-controls="navbarNav"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
          <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#">Home</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#">About</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/user/signup">Sign Up</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="">Login</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="header">About QuickChat</div>
        <div class="sub-header">Connecting people, one chat at a time</div>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            QuickChat is a real-time chat application designed to help you stay
            connected with your friends and family. With seamless messaging,
            media sharing, and video calling features, QuickChat provides a
            comprehensive platform for all your communication needs.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our mission is to make communication simple and accessible for
            everyone. Whether you're catching up with old friends, coordinating
            with colleagues, or just staying in touch with family, QuickChat is
            here to help you communicate effortlessly.
          </p>
          <p>
            We prioritize your privacy and security, ensuring that your
            conversations remain private and secure. Join QuickChat today and
            experience the future of communication.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/user/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="animated-graphic"></div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
